cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper discusses vision-based path following for robots in unstructured outdoor environments. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper relies on colour-constant imaging for accurate path following. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses a deep neural network to predict relative pose for visual odometry and localization. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of AI techniques for path following. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the use of a system for path following in robots.
